title: Vices Theme, with Woman Smoking

description: Oblong, with curved sides and corners, featuring raised decoration representing a variety of vices, including woman in profile smoking, the cigarette smoke extending up and around parts of the background, at bottom is long serpent, above on left are playing cards, at center champagne bottle, at right a champagne glass, on lid are 2 racing horses, identical decoration on reverse.
